<div class="content">
  External Services allow you to copy files from and to a server
  automatically.
  We support HTTP, FTP, SFTP, Dropbox, YouTube, SoundCloud, Amazon S3,
  Archive.org and Libsyn.
  <br> <br>
  Please register additional services in our web interface using the link below!
</div>

<ul>
  <li><a href="{{url}}" class="share"><span></span>Add an external service</a></li>
</ul>

{{#if services}}
  <h1>Your External Services</h1>
  <ul>
    {{#each services}}
      <li><label><span class="light">{{display_type}}</span> <small>{{display_name}}</small></label></li>
    {{/each}}
  </ul>
{{/if}}
